snippet.title: [N64] Midway's Greatest Arcade Hits Volume 1
snippet.description: So bold of them to say "Volume 1" when they didn't make a volume 2. Robotron is probably the best old midway game, IMO. And I don't know how much replay value this would have, even in 2000.
